com.netflix.governator

Interface ProvisionMetrics

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NullProvisionMetrics, SimpleProvisionMetrics

    public interface ProvisionMetrics
    Interface invoked by LifecycleModule's ProvisionListener to gather metrics on objects as they are provisioned. Through the provision listener it's possible to generate a dependency tree for the first initialization of all objects. Note that no call will be made for singletons that are being injected but have already been instantiated.
    Author:
    elandau
